Package: wpgdata
Title: Access the Winnipeg Open Data Portal
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Myo Minn", "Oo", , "dr.myominnoo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4089-016X"))
Description: A tidy interface to the City of Winnipeg Open Data Portal
    (<https://data.winnipeg.ca>). Discover available datasets, inspect
    column schemas, and download records with automatic multi-page
    pagination — all via the Socrata OData V4 and Discovery APIs.
    Supports server-side filtering, column selection, and row ordering
    to minimise data transfer.
